data.description: Welcome home to Oak Grove Island .. This move in ready 4 bedroom residence has been meticulously maintained by the current owners. As you enter the home you can see the open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, kitchen, and sunroom. The eat in kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, solid surface countertops, pantry, eat in bar, and breakfast nook. The primary bedroom is very spacious with access to the sunroom. The primary bathroom boasts a large walk in closet with built in wood shelving, double vanities with lots of storage, nice size walk in shower, with separate jetted tub. The 3 guest rooms are adequately sized with good closet space in each. The sunroom has been enclosed and heated/cooled and is a great place to entertain while out back grilling out on the patio. The back yard is fenced in and offers plenty of privacy. Oak Grove Island is a gated community and offers a community pool, tennis court, and playground. Buyer to measure sq footage during due diligence if exact measurements are important due to enclosing of sunroom.
